Triphone model 

1. HLEd -A -D -T 1 -n triphones1 -l '*' -i wintri.mlf mktri.led aligned.mlf

This creates 2 files:
  
1. wintri.mlf (triphone multi label file)
2. triphones1 (list of triphones in your training set)

2. edit the triphone1 file

sil
l1_i+l1_u
l1_u-l1_i+l2_i 
l1_u-l1_i+l2_u
l1_u+l1_i
l1_i-l1_u+l2_i
